figure.sourcecode:
input: float v // time value output: int a, b // mantissa, exponent of time code
(a, b) encode (v):
if (v == 0) return (0, 0)
if (v < 2 * C) // subnormal a = floor (v * 4 / C) // round down return (a, 0) else // normalized if (v > (1 + 7/8) * 2^31 * C) // check bounds return (7, 31) // return maximum else b = floor (log2(v / C)) // round down a = floor ((v / (2^b * C) - 1) * 8) // round down return (a, b)
